text: Olena Rodina (born 17 May 1975) is a Ukrainian cross-country skier. She competed in three events at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Ukraine Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
